1. Enter email address
2. Enter Password
3. Enter courseID i.e. ex. ml-2012-002
4. Enter Path where you want to download videos to i.e. ex. /home/ninja/Desktop
5. On Desktop it creates a folder named ml-2012-002 and downloads all videos to that folder

Or

1. Create a file ~/.cousera
Put the following entries
user = username
pass = password

2. Run ./CourseraScript.py course-id directory_path

